<table-wrap id="tbl2" orientation="portrait" position="float">
<label>2</label>
<caption>
<title>Comparison
of pK<sub>a</sub> Values<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref60"></xref> of Ligands Used
in the Synthesis of Pillared
MOFs</title>
</caption>
<oasis:table colsep="0" rowsep="0">
<oasis:tgroup cols="3">
<oasis:colspec align="left" colname="col1"></oasis:colspec>
<oasis:colspec align="left" colname="col2"></oasis:colspec>

<oasis:thead>
<oasis:row>

<sub>a</sub>

<oasis:tbody>
<oasis:row>
<oasis:entry>M-DMOF-TM</oasis:entry>
<oasis:entry>TMBDC, DABCO</oasis:entry>

</oasis:row>
<oasis:row>

<oasis:row>
<oasis:entry>M-BTTB-BPY</oasis:entry>

<oasis:entry>4.01, 4.60</oasis:entry>
</oasis:row>
</oasis:tbody>
</oasis:tgroup>
</oasis:table>

Table 2. Comparison of pK<sub>a</sub> Values[^60] of Ligands Used in the Synthesis of Pillared MOFs

| MOF         | ligand       | p<sub>K<sub>a</sub></sub> |
|-------------|--------------|---------------------------|
| M-DMOF-TM   | TMBDC, DABCO | 3.80, 8.86                |
| M-BTTB-DMBPY| BTTB, DMBPY  | 4.01, 5.60                |
| M-BTTB-BPY  | BTTB, BPY    | 4.01, 4.60                |
